rows.label: qst200901_msg001
rows.name: Come on, guys, we need to get going!

rows.label: qst200901_msg003
rows.name:
Everything'll be sold out if we don't
hurry!

rows.label: qst200901_msg004
rows.name:
What you in so much hurry to
purchase, Kasane?

rows.label: qst200901_msg005
rows.name:
Bread, Hana, bread!
The wondrous bread of fortune,
Lucky Dawn Bread!

rows.label: qst200901_msg015
rows.name:
They make it down at Tilly Bakery,
under the windmill!

rows.label: qst200901_msg006
rows.name:
Bread of fortune...?
Never heard of it.

rows.label: qst200901_msg007
rows.name:
They knead Dawn Hydrangeas in
with the dough when they make it.
It's supposed to bring great luck.

rows.label: qst200901_msg008
rows.name: The lady at the inn told me about it!

rows.label: qst200901_msg010
rows.name:
And if you eat it, you bring luck to
yourself and to those around you!

rows.label: qst200901_msg013
rows.name:
It's one of their most popular items, so
if you don't go first thing in the morning
you've got no chance of getting any!

rows.label: qst200901_msg014
rows.name:
So let's go already! Let's get to Tilly
Bakery before they're all sold out!
